FBIS4-62104 "drsov092_m_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-092 Daily Report 11 May 1994 Tajikistan Militants Cross Pyandzh River at Tajik-Afghan Border Militants Cross Pyandzh River at Tajik-Afghan Border LD1105145094 Moscow INTERFAX in English 1347 GMT 11 May 94 LD1105145094 Moscow INTERFAX English BFN [Text] The Russian Border Defense Troops press service told INTERFAX that a group of armed militants had crossed the Pyandzh River and broken through from Afghanistan to Tajikistan on the section controlled by the Pyandzh Border Guards Tenth detachment. The militants hid themselves in the river bush. The militants were attacked.
